      "Saxum's rezoning request has been postponed three times. The Planning Board was set to hear it May 27, but Saxum asked for a delay. The board pushed it to June 24. Then Saxum asked for another postponement, and the matter is now on hold until the city adopts its new data center zoning rules.",
